<subSubSection pageId="39" pageNumber="40" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="39.[151,1436,151,294]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,358,151,177]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Distribution.</emphasis>
Southeast Queensland, 
<collectingCountry box="[642,828,152,178]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
, Loyalty Is, and 
<collectingCountry box="[1027,1189,152,178]" name="New Zealand" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Davie &amp; Short" authorityYear="1989" box="[1201,1372,152,177]" class="Malacostraca" family="Calappidae" genus="Mursia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="microspina">
<emphasis box="[1201,1372,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">M. microspina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
lives on the continental shelf and continental slope. The 
<collectingCountry box="[743,899,190,216]" name="New Zealand" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
specimens came from samples taken between 
<quantity box="[151,290,229,255]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.3649999999999998" metricValueMax="3.18" metricValueMin="1.55" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" unit="m" value="236.5" valueMax="318.0" valueMin="155.0">155–318 m</quantity>
, but the exact upper limit of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Davie &amp; Short" authorityYear="1989" box="[643,818,229,254]" class="Malacostraca" family="Calappidae" genus="Mursia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="microspina">
<emphasis box="[643,818,229,254]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">M. microspina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the shallowest sample is uncertain and could be anywhere from 
<quantity box="[336,472,268,294]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.175" metricValueMax="2.8" metricValueMin="1.55" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" unit="m" value="217.5" valueMax="280.0" valueMin="155.0">
155– 
<specimenCount box="[393,472,268,294]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" type="generic">280 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
. Depth range is 
<quantity box="[662,797,268,294]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.1" metricValueMax="4.2" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" unit="m" value="310.0" valueMax="420.0" valueMin="200.0">
200– 
<specimenCount box="[720,797,268,294]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" type="generic">420 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
